response: {"Q0":"Generally there were some categories I prioritized more and figured more people would desire, such as average lifespan of a product. In many of the cases, it was a choice between better lifespan or better something else at the same proportion(like screen size), in which case I went with the one with better lifespan. Additionally, for some I went with the more well rounded choice, such as with processing speed/memory, as I felt that people would rather have a well rounded device rather than a laptop with insanely high memory but almost no processing speed. strategy_response: Generally there were some categories I prioritized more and figured more people would desire, such as average lifespan of a product. In many of the cases, it was a choice between better lifespan or better something else at the same proportion(like screen size), in which case I went with the one with better lifespan. Additionally, for some I went with the more well rounded choice, such as with processing speed/memory, as I felt that people would rather have a well rounded device rather than a laptop with insanely high memory but almost no processing speed.
